             <h1> About Cindy </h>
         
                 <p> Cindy is a cruiser. This is her first love. Cruising is enjoyable for many people for many reasons. It's a chance for you to disconnect
                 from work or a hectic schedule and reconnect with your playful side. In general, cruises are meant to make passengers happy, and the frequently 
                 feature nightly entertainment, a variety of onboard activities, variety in stops and all the food you could eat. However sometimes adventures 
                 have to take on another form outside of the sea and the RV is her next option of choice. </p> 
                 
